skins.selfIntroduction: The lead ship of the 1936B-class is none other than me, though there were only three of us to begin with... I carried out many artillery and minelaying operations in the Baltic Sea, but in the end, accidentally ran into our own mines along with Z36. Yes, the same as this one down here... Eh? Why is it here?!
skins.acquisition: Commander, my fellow fleetmembers, hello~! I am the singing and dancing Z35! Pleased to meet you!
skins.login: Hallihallo~ Commander, did you dream of me last night?
skins.details: Huh? Commander, why are you in my room? ...Eh?! I'm the one who got the room wrong?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, look look, a bunny! Isn't it so cute?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Just before, I went to see the Lexington sisters' Konzert. You can definitely tell that they are professionals.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, what kind of performance do you like? Tell me so I can go learn it~
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander, what's the matter? Eh, I made a mistake on this document? ...Ah, it's true! Oops, sorry~
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander, I might be playing it cool, but you've already lost my affection points.

skins.shipDescription: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschbl¨¹te!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!
